   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Genele dnd ntuneric</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Voluptos cutturii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iar gropiele cochete</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dulci rd la mijlocul gurii.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Doa Sol </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P45"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Te rog rmi o clip nc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca s te strng duios la piept.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Din fericirea mea adnc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">A vrea s nu m mai detept.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i totui, luna iese-n zare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Albete zidul nalt i gol...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">D-mi cea din urm srutare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i nc una, Doa Sol!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P64"><text:span text:style-name="T4">M-ntrebi cu ochiul tu cuminte</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Unde m duc i ce m fac,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd de pe ceruri stele sfinte</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ptrund n codru, bat n lac.</text:span></text:p>
